{"tid":1583510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果日報 2019 PDF","createTime":"2019-09-20T15:40:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T04:20:48.000Z","uid":55597,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"7ac366c6a56c83c77431c70aca9c1ece5b165f3a","tid":1583510,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:40:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1iZfI7X1ciUyLJggYsOeV-GG5TMto_8sV/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1iZfI7X1ciUyLJggYsOeV-GG5TMto_8sV%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG1%2FFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=900f40c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1iZfI7X1ciUyLJggYsOeV-GG5TMto_8sV/view?usp=sharing</a>"},{"pid":"a5c6990e4808cbffc8182f2fbd65f39e490cf74a","tid":1583510,"uid":284480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rfU3L2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrfU3L2d.jpg&h=35196789&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0b480a5b48e497ebdfe76d2b985d28ec4b83b68","tid":1583510,"uid":265221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:41:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府</span></span>借減碳排放為名，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要向中國買電</span></span><br />\n<br />\n「長遠減碳策略公眾參與」詻詢<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日截止</span></span><br />\n快啲將你既意見SEND EMAIL去：  comments@susdev.org.hk<br />\n<br />\n✏參考意見✏<br />\n<br />\n致可持續發展委員會成員：<br />\n<br />\n「長遠減碳策略公眾參與」諮詢中，當局建議以「 更緊密的區域合作」向中國購買零排放電力，然而本港電力穩定度遠高於中國南方電網，擔心向中國買電會帶來電力不穩，影響本港金融、航運、交通、以至市民日常生活。<br />\n<br />\n此外，《巴黎協定》為一些面積小、欠缺天然資源的小島嶼發展中國家(Small Island Developing States,SIDS) 如新加坡、斐濟等，可因應它們特殊情況，制訂關於溫室氣體低排放發展的策略。<br />\n由於香港地少人多，局限可再生能源發展，亦缺乏天然資源，可選擇的減排策略有限，與其他小島嶼發展中國家情況面臨同樣的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n就此本人有以下意見：<br />\n<br />\n一. 聯網供電會損害供電穩定，故此反對進一步向中國買電，反對採取更緊密的區域合作，香港應以本地發電為主，確保電力穩定；<br />\n二. 遵照2014年未來發電燃料組合諮詢，增加本地天然氣發電及可再生能源比例，代替區域聯網；<br />\n三. 爭取香港以地區名義，直接向政府間氣候變化專門委員會(IPCC)匯報減排策略；<br />\n四. 爭取以發展中國家/地區(Small Island Developing States) 名義，因應香港的情況，以更彈性的方式履行《巴黎協定》；<br />\n五. 放緩人口增長，收緊移民政策，減低整體耗電量；<br />\n六. 制訂具體香港再工業化政策，加強本港農業及回收業的支援，減少貨物入口時的碳排放。"},{"pid":"bac360e54d302a47b911c48b38e89a4e3c2e452d","tid":1583510,"uid":35296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:41:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520ee0ac46b9d9dac0dbcbee3638190abb417136","tid":1583510,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:48:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"d092a7c5a6f7b681975c2bbc1e03fffe20875ec1","tid":1583510,"uid":311701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:53:30.000Z","msg":"多謝你巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"725dcf2d114561c1e86de09447203fc7aa57b255","tid":1583510,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:55:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">The history of Hong Kong</span>"},{"pid":"4d07252e63261f647a55cc618fb97aa7ae75aa0b","tid":1583510,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T15:57:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"170da0201b8d17a36a9d6086